# Auto-Instrumentation for {{.ServiceName}} (Go)

## Install the OpenTelemetry auto-instrumentation agent:

```bash
go get go.opentelemetry.io/auto
```

## Set environment variables:

```bash
export OTEL_SERVICE_NAME={{.ServiceName}}
export OTEL_EXPORTER_OTLP_ENDPOINT=http://localhost:4318
export OTEL_RESOURCE_ATTRIBUTES=service.name={{.ServiceName}}
```

## Run your application with auto-instrumentation:

```bash
go run -a -toolexec="go.opentelemetry.io/auto" main.go
```

